query:
SELECT
            DATE_TRUNC('minute', created_at) - (EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM created_at)::INT % 15) * INTERVAL '1 minute' AS created_at,
            COUNT(*) as count
        FROM
            market_order
        WHERE 
            expires_at > NOW()
        GROUP BY
            DATE_TRUNC('minute', created_at) - (EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM created_at)::INT % 15) * INTERVAL '1 minute'
        ORDER BY
            created_at DESC
